eNCA reporter Ayesha Ismail has the details. #DStv403  JOHANNESBURG - eNCA aired a story about a Western Cape matriculant who achieved six Distinctions. Close to 100% for Maths, Physical Science and Life Sciences. However, we were alerted to the fact that Ambesiwe Mbana had lied. She presented her former classmate’s results as hers. eNCA reporter Ayesha Ismail went back to speak to her and also spoke to the real top achiever.